    "description": "<strong>DISCORD:</strong> <br><br>Step-by-Step 是一款你不能停止奔跑的平台游戏。利用不同的奔跑速度、跳跃高度和弹跳力墙来绕过障碍，到达地图顶端！与朋友一起或独自享受攀爬的乐趣。但一定要小心，因为有些跳跃的难度比其他跳跃来得更高...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361080/extras/0029c5ce003d2d0efa40e10790fbde7b.poster.avif?t=1730771163\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361080/extras/0029c5ce003d2d0efa40e10790fbde7b.webm?t=1730771163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361080/extras/0029c5ce003d2d0efa40e10790fbde7b.mp4?t=1730771163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>极具挑战性但又令人上瘾的游戏玩法！</strong><br><br>虽然你不能停止前进奔跑，但可以按住 <strong>“慢速”</strong> 键或 <strong>“加速”</strong> 键来调整奔跑速度，碰到墙壁可以转身（无论你是否愿意）。此外，还会遇到有趣的修饰符，如&quot;动力墙&quot;，它可让你踢墙弹开，获得巨大的速度提升！独自或与朋友一起在危险的区域进行精确跳跃。而且有手绘艺术，你将在环境优美、色彩丰富的动画和特效中穿梭！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361080/extras/746edc1ba3ec602cd829f33c1c1d595f.poster.avif?t=1730771163\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361080/extras/746edc1ba3ec602cd829f33c1c1d595f.webm?t=1730771163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361080/extras/746edc1ba3ec602cd829f33c1c1d595f.mp4?t=1730771163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>别害怕摔倒...</strong><br><br>无论是分心还是失误，摔倒都是不可避免的。由于没有检查点和即时自动保存，你将必须重新攀爬，再次尝试跳跃。摔跤摔得较小时，不会惩罚你，其他的则可能不那么宽容。不过不用担心！难度从简单开始，随着时间的推移会逐渐增加，这意味着游戏适合各种技能水平的玩家！你将在底部磨练自己的技能，以便克服上方的障碍。当你接近顶部时，你将感到前所未有的肾上腺素和兴奋！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361080/extras/49ca2fdc1358dee252b9d5de71c0554d.poster.avif?t=1730771163\" width=620 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361080/extras/49ca2fdc1358dee252b9d5de71c0554d.webm?t=1730771163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361080/extras/49ca2fdc1358dee252b9d5de71c0554d.mp4?t=1730771163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>与朋友</strong>一起挑战更精彩！<br><br>谁不喜欢嘲笑朋友的缺点呢？自定义你的角色，让您在竞争中脱颖而出！<br><br>在线功能：<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 朋友的名字会以绿色突出显示！</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 自定义你的角色！</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 旁观朋友的游戏！</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 隐藏不在你的好友列表中的玩家！</li></ul>",
